    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Dor of Chicago has made arrange\nments on an extensive scale for the\nreception at the Auditorium tonight\nin honor of John Mitchell. president\nof the United Mine Workers of\nAmerica.\n\n\nBesides Mr.. Mitchell. the guests of\nhonor will include Clarence Darrow\nand Henry ID. Lloyd, attorneys for\nthe union miners of the anthracite\nregion before the arbitration board."
    }
